{
  "stem": "27767.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In '40, when they came into Hungarian, two weeks later they put him into jail for a few weeks, four weeks or so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they had all kinds of things with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, we were restricted already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't leave the town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said that time, you can't leave the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and you have to wear the star all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was about from April-- beginning of April, we wear the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then two, three weeks after that, about three weeks after that, in one early morning, they came to our house, one detective-- Hungarian detective, which was part of the authorities there who came from main Hungary, and two policemen.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they brought with them some Hungarian Levente.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the young Hungarians who they used for this to help them with the deportation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Levente.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Levente, like here, the scout-- the scout boys, or the Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-E-V-E-N-T-E, t as in Thomas, E, Levente.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called them Leventes, like Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were like 15, 16, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They supposed to make sure everybody is caught up with them, and taken out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they came about 6:00, or 5:30 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first thing this guy, the detective, gave me a-- hit me on the face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they gave us half an hour to put together some food and some-- but, initially, they-- we prepared already, because they said they will-- we heard some rumors they were taking away us, they were taking away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother prepared food, and all kinds of foods, and cakes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had big bags prepared with all kind of clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
